{"tid":2037900,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大year 1 engine仔同我入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-05-27T08:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T17:48:11.000Z","uid":316647,"like":5,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"cc8865bbf42fb3c93d417cf9d81e035a83cf5705","tid":2037900,"uid":316647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T08:48:10.000Z","msg":"大家都知1130 final個分出咗，問過好多人，滿分100冇一個人高過30分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有見及此，小弟draft咗一份email打算send比Anthony So(Associate Dean of Student Affairs in the Faculty of Engineering)去appeal grade<br />\n我知有好多連登仔已經放棄咗呢科，仲好熱心咁狙擊麥博士，但係呢份email係想比真係有認真讀、擺過心機落去，為咗下年入到個好major嘅人去appeal，如果你都係好比心機但係個分低到hihi而覺得好唔抵嘅話，歡迎你一齊appeal<br />\n其他鍵盤戰士可以出返去，呢度冇你嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一mail，多啲人send email先可以令faculty注意到個問題！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nDraft如下，改一改就可以send，咁當然亦都歡迎大家自己加野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟英文差，如果有咩問題希望各位可以大方提出！<br />\n<br />\nAnthony So個email: manchoso@se.cuhk.edu.hk<br />\n<br />\nGrade Appeal Request for ENGG1130 Test 2<br />\n<br />\nDear Dr. So, <br />\n<br />\nMy name is Chan Siu Ming (student ID: 1155000000) and I am a year one board-based Engineering student. Last Saturday (May 23) I received the score of ENGG1130 Test 2 via Blackboard and I am not satisfied with the result. I believe there were some situations that were beyond my control that contributed to my low score. With utmost humbleness, I am writing to request that my written test 2 script to be reviewed and graded again. <br />\n<br />\n I understand that Dr. Mak did his best helping us to obtain good grades and pass the course, I am also aware of the fact that Dr. Mak has been under great pressure throughout this term. I would like to express my appreciation to Dr. Mak&rsquo;s contributions to this course, he is a patient and enthusiastic teacher. Under his instruction, I have gained a lot of useful knowledge in Multivariable Calculus. <br />\n<br />\n However, I do not think I deserve a score of XX for test 2. <br />\n<br />\nI worked extremely hard in this course and on this test. I know there are a lot of websites for students to pay and get the solutions for their homework from mathematics experts. However, I insisted on finishing all the assessments by myself and with my fellow students, on average, I usually spend xx days to finish one homework, and I received favorable scores. And so I have strong reasons to believe that I can handle this course and obtain a good grade as long as I try my best on every task, test, and exam. <br />\n<br />\nIn the preparation for the midterm test and the test 2, I revised for xx days in total, used up countless papers as scratch papers and notes, watched the Panopto videos and read the lecture notes on Blackboard over and over. Therefore, with my effort and based on the scores I obtained for the homework, I expected that I can obtain a score higher than xx that truly reflects my effort, instead of a score of xx. <br />\n<br />\nSecondly, this year&rsquo;s CGPA is very important to me. We board-based students have to compete with each other in order to get into our preferred engineering major next year. My first preference is xxx, I know it is not easy to be admitted to xxx therefore I worked very hard, hoping that I can become a xxx student in September. <br />\n<br />\nFor the above reasons, therefore, I am making a request that my written test 2 script to be checked and reviewed again, and the score to be raised. Thank you for considering my request and I apologize for any inconvenience caused. <br />\n<br />\nBest Regards,<br />\nChan Siu Ming<br />\nMay 27, 2020<br />\n<br />\n最後，已經嚟到最後一刻，N賤仔如果再唔去爭取嘅話就咩都冇，希望大家踴躍send email"},{"pid":"78a256f2f9d450225dcd26256f469600cc5ae1fa","tid":2037900,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T08:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea21a9acca6f64c7ee6bf43bc44c46080adc125","tid":2037900,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T08:50:56.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"a612bb2e2e7f4b45f78d7d5ee24680f457e6992b","tid":2037900,"uid":208823,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"知唔知班nds幾分? 如果nds都得5 60 即係卷嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n如果nds有8 90分 咁無得講 能力問題"},{"pid":"06ac605c7bf1953cebeaa974f34abe7902b1959a","tid":2037900,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bd319f795c8a4c5ce6e8476162825b5e78479c6","tid":2037900,"uid":199408,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:15:26.000Z","msg":"Online exam唔洗你開cam 份份卷都出到勁難 又真係得一個hugo有問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0cb10c7ff66d025e8feccd43a704d631fe25eb","tid":2037900,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:15:39.000Z","msg":"召喚數學傻閪Hugo Mak"},{"pid":"ece1596f17ff961dc9c70de996fa9e244575c9f1","tid":2037900,"uid":45914,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:15:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a1a7d06837d6ee575ed11a5f84a35078c5ea1c2","tid":2037900,"uid":316647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3bd319f795c8a4c5ce6e8476162825b5e78479c6","tid":2037900,"uid":199408,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:15:26.000Z","msg":"Online exam唔洗你開cam 份份卷都出到勁難 又真係得一個hugo有問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"我地係要開cam架ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im