\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9888528593c43cbc3550dcf6d01422641f3b2dd9","tid":2037900,"uid":310933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"好奇各位工程新生係唔係認為繼續比Hugo出功課出卷同改功課改卷無問題，我地花生小組在食花生既過程中，發現Hugo根本係__中既__，我地就完全唔放心比佢教啦。<br />\n<br />\n等我地講下佢邊幾方面有問題啦~<br />\n<br />\n============PART 1: Integrity============<br />\n<br />\na. IMO<br />\n感謝某位lecturer既答覆證實左我地食既花生係真既，Hugo的確在2015年國際數學奧林匹克香港選拔賽初賽（IMO Prelim）中涉嫌洩漏試卷比自己train既math team，事後IMO禁止Hugo參與任何IMO相關的訓練和比賽。而香港另外三大數學比賽&mdash;&mdash;香港數學奧林匹克（HKMO）、香港青少年數學精英選拔賽和培正數學邀請賽亦同時永久blacklist Hugo。<br />\n呢件事佢好彩無上到報，但當年其他人的同情心，放過佢一馬，就被比到一個有洩漏試題前科既math trainner有機會入到嚟CU Engine教書兼且出卷<br />\n<br />\nb. Journal<br />\n如果各位有追連登既post，你會發現Hugo喺我地開始討論佢嘅orcid 18分鐘後突然private左，好明顯佢orcid有問題。感謝萬能的google有backup，比我地發現到佢有幾篇journal係有問題<br />\n<br />\n- Engineering Cell Surfaces via Liposome Fusion.<br />\n呢篇journal既Issue Date係14 Nov 2011，Author係Dutta D, Pulsipher A, Luo W, Mak H, Yousaf MN，Hugo當時仲讀緊中學，但佢在orcid認領為自己既作品（唔會係唔小心或疏於打理，睇埋後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。<br />\n真。Hugo Mak既身分係一個2011年UG grad既York University學生。<br />\n<br />\n- Minimization of Optical Rogue Waves Formation based on Hamiltonian approach<br />\n呢篇Journal既source係To Physics Journal, v. 1, (1), 2018，屬於Purkh<br />\n&ldquo;Purkh is an open-access journal which means that all content is freely available without charge to the user or his/her institution. Users are allowed to read, download, copy, distribute, print, search, or link to the full texts of the articles in this journal without asking prior permission from the publisher or the author.<br />\nMoreover, Purkh charges a modest Purkh fee to authors that are based on a sliding scale, providing reduced rates for low and middle-income countries.&rdquo;<br />\n好明顯係一個predatory journal（即係你比錢佢，就算係一篇垃圾佢都會幫你出，eg: &quot;Get Me Off Your Fucking Mailing List&quot; is an actual science paper accepted by a journal）有興趣既同學可以search下 &ldquo;Giving Birth to Vectorial Coordinate Geometry&rdquo; 呢篇都係under Purkh既MathLAB，佢篇文基本上就係prove下y=mx+c同y-y1=m(x-x1) 呢d中學野<br />\n<br />\n- Tackling Geometry Problems in Mathematics Competition Hong Kong Joint School Society-Math Journal<br />\n無錯，Google顯示Hugo將HKJSMS newsletter中佢做左一條數mark為Journal，證明到Hugo的確精心打理過佢既orcid，如果唔係點會比佢入到orcid profile兼mark為journal？"},{"pid":"7a464f94d701fddebdc31afea392d9d1d405c687","tid":2037900,"uid":210291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:39:45.000Z","msg":"讀得中大engine嘅差唔多啦"},{"pid":"c02086791fb943f75c7e9df6a1ec2fb7975f9d20","tid":2037900,"uid":310933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"============PART 2: Grading============<br />\n<br />\n呢一科係用absolute grading，Hugo有心可以刻意出到份卷好難/cut-off高到上天花板<br />\n- 從Homework 2可見，Hugo絕對有能力在呢件事熱度稍降後，將功課/考試回復到Homework 2的難度（甚至更高），或是和Homework 2一樣未學先做<br />\n- 關於absolute grading方面，理論上Hugo係可以做到咁樣嘅cut-off<br />\nA 100<br />\nA- 99<br />\nB 96-98<br />\nC 93-95<br />\nD+ 92<br />\nD 30-91<br />\n- 根據中大既「處理學生投訴程序」：對教師的學術判斷或評核持有異議而提出的投訴，則將不獲受理。<br />\n- 事實上，校方甚少會干預教師的學術判斷。<br />\n- 到時出左grade最多比你appeal，而所謂的上訴程序從來都冇同學諗得咁透明，而你覺得有用？龍門任Hugo搬架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係我就唔放心比佢改卷啦。唔知你有冇信心你在大大小小既Homework、Quiz、Midterm和Final入面一次都唔會被Hugo屈到？定係你相信 &ldquo;Professor Anthony So, in his capacity of the Engineering Mathematics Subject Panel Convener, will monitor the teaching of the course. He will sit in the lectures and ensure the appropriateness of the assessments and fairness in grading.&rdquo;？講多少少，ENGG1130一個course最少500人，Anthony有冇咁嘅心力毅力去睇哂咁多份卷或者course content有冇問題？如果唔係就唔洗專登搵一班teaching team嚟幫手啦？搵個人嚟cross check幾百份卷，我地就唔信Anthony有咁多時間同心機啦。<br />\n==================================<br />\n<br />\n條路自己揀，_____。你想唔想要major？你甘心因為1130一科爛GPA而去唔到exchange兼攞唔到scholar？<br />\n<br />\n我地成條team用左至少四日三夜搜證，希望工程系新生唔好將我地的血汗付諸東流。<br />\n<br />\n以上所有說法皆有證據，感謝Google和佢既萬能backup，仲有某位lecturer提供的關鍵證據。<br />\n<br />\nJustice must be done and upheld! (Mak, 2020)"},{"pid":"41a00486e891ae9799c7a035734c46de6728b7d4","tid":2037900,"uid":310933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:40:29.000Z","msg":"Tony：「在戰隊hugo常常痛駡一些年輕選手，這再正常不過了，不過也有選手被激怒的時候，記得在一場熱身賽中場休息的時候，hugo前幾場打得很不自在，回到更衣室用水瓶怒砸一位才進戰隊的選手，當時很多隊友都已經無法容忍hugo的所作所為，再加上那些常被他欺辱的隊友，無法阻止的一幕發生了，至少有10人群毆了hugo，你可以想像被10人群毆的滋味，在一旁的hugo更是拍手叫好，不停大喊：『給我打，把他往死裡打！』當時chris、tony這兩位大佬並沒有參與這次毆鬥，他們也沒有阻止，好像一切與他倆無關。」"},{"pid":"4e91b5dc789a55c0bb269d70359bfb41825cc3e8","tid":2037900,"uid":40867,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n冇人過30 你話係就係啊？<br />\n<br />\n係咪自己圍內d on9 小圈子ocamp group 問一句<br />\n然後上連登先發現物以類聚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThere were some loser that were輸唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要話nds得50都唔正常 <br />\n高你一半啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要人人同你一樣咁廢先開心咩"},{"pid":"59ed6435d2d86a0c85de5907b457b10d9509506b","tid":2037900,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0830cf41738abc01fad27559347a82d4b4df64d","tid":2037900,"uid":200521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d13c57daf37b5d179ccf7f63aa113ccf085c154","tid":2037900,"uid":316647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"242d6f2583b6be2dad3f8134893aa509dfcd53b8","tid":2037900,"uid":200521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:26:09.000Z","msg":"冇人高過30？咪鳩吹喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"我話我知嘅人姐 你就話我鳩吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:34:50.000Z","msg":"咁係你識得人少。<img src=